---
title: Honey Miso Sweet Potato Poke Bowl with Pickled Carrot, Tenderstem® Broccoli and Peanuts
description: Our Honey Miso Sweet Potato Squash Rice Poke Bowl is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R20_W17_UK_V12674-9_Main_low-d52ad05c.jpg
